<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>🎉 Birthday Surprise 🎉</title>

<style>
body{
    margin:0;
    font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff9ad5,#ffd166,#7bdff2);
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    height:100vh;
    text-align:center;
    color:#fff;
}

.card{
    background:rgba(0,0,0,.35);
    padding:35px;
    border-radius:20px;
    max-width:450px;
}

button{
    padding:12px 28px;
    font-size:18px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:30px;
    margin:10px;
    cursor:pointer;
}

#surprise{
    display:none;
    margin-top:20px;
    animation:fade 1s;
}

@keyframes fade{
from{opacity:0;}
to{opacity:1;}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

<h1>🎁 Someone sent you a Birthday Surprise!</h1>

<p>Would you like to open it?</p>

<button onclick="openGift()">YES 🎉</button>
<button onclick="alert('Nice try 😄 You have to open it eventually!')">NO 🙈</button>

<div id="surprise">

<h2>🎂 Happy Birthday, Sarah! 🎂</h2>

<p>
Wishing you a year filled with happiness, laughter,
good health, and amazing memories.
You deserve the very best today and always.
❤️
</p>

<h3>🎈 Surprise Gift</h3>

<p>🍰 A virtual birthday cake just for you!</p>

<p style="font-size:70px;">🎂🎉🎁🎈</p>

</div>

</div>

<script>
function openGift(){
document.getElementById("surprise").style.display="block";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
